- Croftfield. "C Bar".

64
00:15:39,124 --> 00:15:42,503
Vraćate se onamo, ha?
- Ne.

65
00:15:45,089 --> 00:15:46,799
Kamo ćete?

66
00:15:48,133 --> 00:15:49,927
U Waco.

67
00:15:51,804 --> 00:15:55,683
Samo vas trojica?
- Da, trojica smo.

68
00:15:57,184 --> 00:16:00,104
Vas je petorica?
- Da.

69
00:16:01,063 --> 00:16:05,859
Jeste li vidjeli Kiowa
indijance na rijeci Pea?

70
00:16:06,485 --> 00:16:08,904
Dvoje, troje.

71
00:16:08,988 --> 00:16:11,574
Većinom samo tragove.

72
00:16:32,636 --> 00:16:34,221
Uđi.

73
00:16:37,224 --> 00:16:42,479
Upravo sam Otisu i Vernu
govorio kako je Adam pao na nož.

74
00:16:47,318 --> 00:16:50,905
Napijte se.
- Hvala.

75
00:17:18,891 --> 00:17:22,311
Slobodno se poslužite hranom.
- Hvala.

76
00:17:24,355 --> 00:17:28,484
Ljudi će noćas
prespavati ovdje, Edgare.

77
00:17:33,614 --> 00:17:35,658
Uđite, momci.

78
00:17:41,247 --> 00:17:45,834
Momci, ovo su Otis, Vern i...

79
00:17:46,126 --> 00:17:50,923
