145
00:25:59,036 --> 00:26:00,829
Slušaj ovamo!

146
00:26:01,038 --> 00:26:03,832
Opkoljeni ste!
- Prokleti Edgar!

147
00:26:03,832 --> 00:26:08,212
Ne otežavajte položaj!
Nemate šanse!

148
00:26:11,340 --> 00:26:13,300
Što ćemo sada, Dick?

149
00:26:13,509 --> 00:26:17,137
