00:26:26,897 --> 00:26:29,149
Nemate nikakve šanse!

153
00:26:39,159 --> 00:26:42,162
Nećemo čekati zauvijek!

154
00:26:48,127 --> 00:26:51,338
Otvaramo vatru na tri!

155
00:26:54,133 --> 00:26:55,718
